{"title":"BTCHN’ Bikes Titanium Drop Bar V2 Is Customizable!","link":"https://theradavist.com/btchn-bikes-titainium-drop-bar/","date":1747828804000,"content":"<p><em>First debuted at <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2023-made-bike-show-coverage-part-02/#:~:text=BTCHN%20Bikes%20Titanium%20Randonneur\" target=\"_blank\">2023 Made Bike Show</a> on Tyler’s personal über weight weenie randonneur, the BTCHN’ Bikes Titanium Drop Bar is back and better than ever with V2…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-11.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-11.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-11.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-11.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-9.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-9.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-8.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-8.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Alright, here we go… the new titanium drop bar from BTCHN’. This is something Tyler from BTCHN’ has been dreaming about for YEARS, and is so damn pumped to release the latest version. The real magic? The 3D printed corners. These bad boys let us dial in ergonomic shapes that traditional manufacturing just can’t pull off.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-12.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-12.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-12.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-12.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>And the best part? You get to fully customize them: pick your width, your flare, made just for YOU. This is <em>your</em> bar, made to fit exactly the way you want it because you’re gonna spend countless hours riding with it. It should feel like a second home.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-13.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-13.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-13.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-13.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Think of these titanium drop bars like a completely custom riding experience for your favorite bike. Yes, they start at $620 but titanium is expensive, 3D printed parts are expensive, and time is expensive, but <a href=\"https://youtu.be/dL93SiRl89s?si=4Jf3uPB9xfQSb0mx&amp;t=398\" target=\"_blank\">titanium is IMMMORRRRTAL</a>!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-17.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-17.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-17.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-17.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-27.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-27.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-27.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-27.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Titanium’s the real deal. When it comes to handlebars, it’s got this incredible mix of forgiveness and durability that no other material can match. The ovalized top section gives you a bigger surface for your palms, making long rides smoother and more comfortable. All while staying aero—yeah, it’s that good. Win-win.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-18.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-18.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-18.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-18.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The first 30 orders will ship by June 21st, so don’t sleep on it!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-16.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-16.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-16.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/BTCHN-BIKES-TITANIUM-DROP-BARS-16.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>31.8mm Clamp Diameter</li>\n<li>73mm Reach</li>\n<li>107mm Drop</li>\n<li>Custom Width: 34cm – 50cm (Hood to hood width)</li>\n<li>Custom Flare: 8°, 15°, or 25°</li>\n<li>Weight:\n<ul>\n<li>40cm: 370g</li>\n<li>42cm: 377g</li>\n<li>44cm: 384g</li>\n<li>46cm: 391g</li>\n<li>Etc etc.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Pre-order now at <a href=\"https://www.btchnbikes.com/components/btchn-ti-drop-bar\" target=\"_blank\">BTCHN’ BIKES</a>!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/btchn-bikes-titainium-drop-bar/\">BTCHN’ Bikes Titanium Drop Bar V2 Is Customizable!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"496babf6130ec8e3e3a900cd2032bb17cd0d72deb3a6165be0062f1b74ca4ad4","category":"Cycling"}